s/music/heres-what-quincy-jones-really-thought-about-the-beatles-and-u2-3809298">粉丝们一直在重新分享琼斯近年来最直言不讳的言论</a>，包括当他将<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">甲壳虫</a>形容为“世界上最糟糕的音乐家”时，当他谈到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/u2">U2</a>何时让他留在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bono">波诺</a>时S城堡“因为爱尔兰是如此的种族主义”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-order-and-peter-hook-pay-tribute-to-quincy-jones-he-made-us-big-in-america-3809451">新命令和彼得·胡克（Peter Hook）向昆西·琼斯（Quincy Jones）致敬：“他让我们在美国大大”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
